entries.femaleVariant: What do you think? Should we take it?
We will have to discuss it. Me, I don't see a problem. Money is money.
I heard they could be here a while. Starting up some modified hydroponics.
So why are we standing here, talking what-ifs? We should make a deal.
Screw yourself. You sure have a lot to say for someone who wasn't there.
Well, how much they offer? If it's not much, I say screw them. I never liked Biotechnica.
